<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ERMFox Portfolio</title>
    <link href="/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-sans">
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow p-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <section class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-rose-600 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
                Effective Date: [Insert Date]
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information I Collect</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                I collect the following data to operate the site and provide my services:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username and hashed passwords for account functionality.</li>
                <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name and email address submitted through the contact form or email.</li>
                <li><strong>Comments:</strong> Contributions to the worldbuilding content associated with your username.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. How I Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>
                I use your information to enable account functionality, respond to inquiries, and improve the user experience. I do not use your data for marketing or advertising purposes.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>
                I do not share, sell, or rent your personal data to third parties. Your information remains private and secure.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>
                I delete all account-related data (except comments, which are anonymized) when an account is deleted. Contact form submissions are deleted after resolving the inquiry.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>
                You have the right to access, update, or request deletion of your data. To exercise these rights, contact me via email or the contact form on this site.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                I implement reasonable measures to protect your data, including password hashing, secure storage, and limited access to personal information.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p>
                This site does not use cookies or third-party tracking for analytics or advertising purposes. Cookies may be used for session management and functionality only.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>
                I may update this policy to reflect changes in my practices or services. Significant changes will be communicated through updates on this page.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>
                For any privacy concerns or to exercise your rights, contact me at:
            </p>
            <a href="mailto:sophie.saa@pm.me" class="text-rose-600 font-semibold hover:underline">sophie.saa@pm.me</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
